result.name: I Know John

reviews.text: Loved the concept and the cocktails that they served. Can’t wait for them to open their new location to enjoy even more creative drinks.

The shape of the bar is a tad weird and hard for big groups to socialise.  It is on entertainer however and will give you buy one get one free for cocktails and house wine.  No specialty cocktails.  The cocktail selection they have are just your average bar cocktails but the offering is decent.
They got the best hh in town
It's closed, don't bother going.
Great, balanced cocktail menu. "23 in fashion" is a must try. Like a rum old fashioned with a chocolate lime twist.
